an indicator of a larger issue.

321
00:27:37,375 --> 00:27:41,150
I agree. Let's pursue
all the cases of pedophilia

322
00:27:41,200 --> 00:27:42,375
that are infesting our Church.

323
00:27:42,425 --> 00:27:43,825
Let's widen the circle.

324
00:27:43,875 --> 00:27:46,950
Let's prosecute all the cases
of homosexuality

325
00:27:47,000 --> 00:27:49,175
that are infesting our Church.

326
